{"type": "article", "id": 30215, "title": "介于鞋与袜之间的装备", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-27T22:59:02Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 47, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160727175946avGtjwSDCRHyWxYi.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>鞋子的款式和功能越来越多，市面上更是出现了不少专门为增强运动表现而设计的鞋子。美中不足的是，有些鞋子可能过多地考虑专业性而牺牲了舒适和轻便。Skinners Technologies 的设计师们为此特别研发了一款介于鞋与袜之间的出行装备 Skinners，底部采用了极耐磨的双层材料，只要穿上它就可以照常进行健身、远足、以及其他锻炼活动。Skinners 仅重 80 克，可以像袜子一样卷起后塞进包里，让你在外出旅行时不用再背着又重又占地方的鞋子。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/skinners-revolutionary-ultraportable-footwear#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，售价为 40 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727180004k6iDCJ5m0u1ohp3s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.716176\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727180005xDb9dsOT6ZLNjl7k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.488235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727180004LKihJu5vpogU8GfX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.488235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160727180005KHYNw4lFpd0nuIQy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.488235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}